So what I am going to do is...

00:00:13.370 --> 00:00:14.430
I will ask you a few questions.

00:00:15.730 --> 00:00:18.010
First, who is involved in this?

00:00:18.050 --> 00:00:19.050
Who are the players?

00:00:22.770 --> 00:00:25.090
I think the two main actors

00:00:25.090 --> 00:00:27.690
are clear.

00:00:27.830 --> 00:00:29.650
On the one hand, we have an advertiser,

00:00:29.770 --> 00:00:31.850
which is the part of the purchase.

00:00:33.130 --> 00:00:36.150
It is someone who seeks to buy

00:00:36.150 --> 00:00:38.250
a advertising space to a certain

00:00:38.250 --> 00:00:40.430
target that has been marked.

00:00:40.850 --> 00:00:42.690
And, on the other hand, we have on the

00:00:42.690 --> 00:00:43.950
other side the part of the sale, which

00:00:44.090 --> 00:00:45.410
are the supports.

00:00:46.310 --> 00:00:47.810
