00:01:00.150 --> 00:01:03.830
mobile app, which has an inventory

00:01:03.830 --> 00:01:06.390
available to those advertisers.

00:01:07.590 --> 00:01:08.830
What is the inventory?

00:01:09.410 --> 00:01:10.370
We would say too.

00:01:10.790 --> 00:01:13.790
The inventory, by definition, is

00:01:13.790 --> 00:01:16.510
the entire space that can receive

00:01:16.510 --> 00:01:18.050
an impact advertising.

00:01:18.310 --> 00:01:20.410
That is, those blank spaces that

00:01:20.410 --> 00:01:22.150
have to be filled by the advertiser

00:01:22.150 --> 00:01:24.130
to unfold their message or

00:01:24.130 --> 00:01:26.410
paint their message to the

00:01:26.410 --> 00:01:27.370
user.

00:01:28.330 --> 00:01:31.450
The inventory would be...

00:01:31.450 --> 00:01:34.310
We are entering an online era.

00:01:35.250 --> 00:01:37.050
