00:01:41.690 --> 00:01:43.610
Inventory is the

00:01:43.610 --> 00:01:45.010
volume of spaces

00:01:45.010 --> 00:01:46.590
that are able

00:01:46.590 --> 00:01:49.690
to offer you in

00:01:49.690 --> 00:01:51.030
a given time.

00:01:51.270 --> 00:01:52.930
And they sell it to me, who am the advertiser.

00:01:53.030 --> 00:01:56.530
To make the advertising impact.

00:01:57.810 --> 00:02:00.930
It is also important that we know

00:02:00.930 --> 00:02:03.830
that there are other actors within

00:02:03.830 --> 00:02:07.750
this equation, such as meters.

00:02:08.210 --> 00:02:10.010
