00:02:10.010 --> 00:02:12.630
certified by the IAB, which is the

00:02:12.630 --> 00:02:13.910
regulatory body of all digital

00:02:13.910 --> 00:02:16.150
advertising, is Comscore.

00:02:16.650 --> 00:02:18.350
Comscore basically does what it

00:02:18.350 --> 00:02:21.790
does is measure the traffic of each

00:02:21.790 --> 00:02:24.990
of those internet properties so

00:02:24.990 --> 00:02:27.150
that it publicly offers us that

00:02:27.150 --> 00:02:28.230
traffic information.

00:02:28.390 --> 00:02:29.830
Traffic is basically the

00:02:29.830 --> 00:02:34.250
volume of traffic impressions

00:02:34.250 --> 00:02:35.850
that each of those properties has.

00:02:36.570 --> 00:02:38.210
We also measure this in

00:02:38.210 --> 00:02:38.930
single users.

00:02:39.270 --> 00:02:40.530
That is, Comscore tells us what

00:02:40.530 --> 00:02:41.710
is amongst many metrics that

00:02:41.710 --> 00:02:43.650
gives us is how many unique users

00:02:43.650 --> 00:02:46.490
have interacted with that

00:02:46.490 --> 00:02:48.530
property in a month.

00:02:49.370 --> 00:02:52.410
The country has had 20 million

00:02:52.410 --> 00:02:53.930
unique users in the world,

00:02:53.930 --> 00:02:56.230
21 brand, 12, etc.

